org.apache.geode.experimental.driver

Interface Region<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - Type of region keys.
    V - Type of region values.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProtobufRegion

    @Experimental
public interface Region<K,V>
    Defines the behaviors of a GemFire region. A region is an associative array from unique keys to values. For each key, the region will contain zero or one value. This code is an experimental prototype and is presented "as is" with no warranty, suitability, or fitness of purpose implied.
    See Also:
    JSONWrapper
